### ==========================================
### PRODUCT — RUTAS PÚBLICAS
### ==========================================

### Get all products SIN parámetros (sin token — público ✅)
GET {{baseUrl}}/product/ HTTP/1.1

### ==========================================

### Página 1 con limit 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/product/?page=1&limit=1 HTTP/1.1

### ==========================================

### GET product by ID (válido ✅)
GET {{baseUrl}}/product/{{productId}} HTTP/1.1

### ==========================================

### ==========================================
### PRODUCT — CREATE (admin + editor)
### ==========================================

### Create product (admin — válido ✅ 201)
POST {{baseUrl}}/product/ HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Pantalon Hombre Basement",
    "description": "Pantalon de hombre",
    "long_description": "Pantalon de hombre de la marca Basement, tela drill",
    "subcategory_id": {{subcategoryId}},
    "brand_id": {{brandId}}
}

### ==========================================

### Create product (editor — válido ✅ 201)
POST {{baseUrl}}/product/ HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{editorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Polo Hombre Basement",
    "description": "Polo de hombre",
    "long_description": "Polo de hombre de la marca Basement, tela algodón",
    "subcategory_id": {{subcategoryId}},
    "brand_id": {{brandId}}
}

### ==========================================

### Create product (customer — 403 ❌)
POST {{baseUrl}}/product/ HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Pantalon Hombre Basement",
    "description": "Pantalon de hombre",
    "long_description": "Pantalon de hombre de la marca Basement",
    "subcategory_id": {{subcategoryId}},
    "brand_id": {{brandId}}
}

### ==========================================

### Create product (sin token — 401 ❌)
POST {{baseUrl}}/product/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Pantalon Hombre Basement",
    "description": "Pantalon de hombre",
    "long_description": "Pantalon de hombre de la marca Basement",
    "subcategory_id": {{subcategoryId}},
    "brand_id": {{brandId}}
}

### ==========================================

### Create product (subcategory_id no existe — 404 ❌)
POST {{baseUrl}}/product/ HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Pantalon Hombre Basement",
    "description": "Pantalon de hombre",
    "long_description": "Pantalon de hombre de la marca Basement",
    "subcategory_id": 999,
    "brand_id": {{brandId}}
}

### ==========================================

### Create product (brand_id no existe — 404 ❌)
POST {{baseUrl}}/product/ HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Pantalon Hombre Basement",
    "description": "Pantalon de hombre",
    "long_description": "Pantalon de hombre de la marca Basement",
    "subcategory_id": {{subcategoryId}},
    "brand_id": 999
}

### ==========================================

### Create product (sin campos requeridos — 422 ❌)
POST {{baseUrl}}/product/ HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Pantalon Hombre Basement"
}


### ==========================================
### PRODUCT — ACTIVATE / DEACTIVATE (admin + editor)
### ==========================================

### Activate product (admin — válido ✅)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/product/{{productId}}/activate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ==========================================

### Activate product (editor — válido ✅)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/product/{{productId}}/activate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{editorToken}}

### ==========================================

### Activate product (customer — 403 ❌)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/product/{{productId}}/activate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### ==========================================

### Activate product (sin token — 401 ❌)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/product/{{productId}}/activate HTTP/1.1

### ==========================================

### Activate product (no existe — 404 ❌)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/product/999/activate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ==========================================

### Deactivate product (admin — válido ✅)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/product/{{productId}}/deactivate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ==========================================

### Deactivate product (editor — válido ✅)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/product/{{productId}}/deactivate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{editorToken}}

### ==========================================

### Deactivate product (customer — 403 ❌)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/product/{{productId}}/deactivate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### ==========================================

### Deactivate product (sin token — 401 ❌)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/product/{{productId}}/deactivate HTTP/1.1

### ==========================================

### Deactivate product (no existe — 404 ❌)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/product/999/deactivate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}